  "detailed_description": "Super Kiwi 64 is a 3D-Platformer and Collect-a-Thon, in a low poly late 90s console look. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n- Low poly late 90s retro looks. <br />\r\n- Kiwi can jump, glide, corkscrew-attack and stick to walls in order to jump up almost every wall.<br />\r\n- The levels can be played in any order, and not every level needs to be finished in order to collect enough to reach the ending. <br />\r\n- Features a bird with a long beak!",
  "about_the_game": "Super Kiwi 64 is a 3D-Platformer and Collect-a-Thon, in a low poly late 90s console look. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n- Low poly late 90s retro looks. <br />\r\n- Kiwi can jump, glide, corkscrew-attack and stick to walls in order to jump up almost every wall.<br />\r\n- The levels can be played in any order, and not every level needs to be finished in order to collect enough to reach the ending. <br />\r\n- Features a bird with a long beak!",
